Flora Original contains the good oils (sunflower oil and canola oi) and combines that great Flora taste with essential fatty acids, and has 65% less saturated fat than butter. With a mission to help people look good, feel good and get more out of life, and a background in nutrition research, Unilever has been at the forefront of developing heart healthy margarine spreads for over 40 years. Pioneering Heart Healthy Spreads - The link between increased consumption of saturated fats and poor heart health was firmly established in the 1950s. Since then Flora products have contained the natural goodness of sunny sunflowers. Sunflower seed oil naturally contains Omega 6 and Vitamin E.
